table.name: auth_group
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "auth_group" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "name" varchar(150) NOT NULL UNIQUE)

table.name: auth_group_permissions
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "auth_group_permissions" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "group_id" integer NOT NULL REFERENCES "auth_group" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "permission_id" integer NOT NULL REFERENCES "auth_permission" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED)

table.name: auth_permission
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "auth_permission" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "content_type_id" integer NOT NULL REFERENCES "django_content_type" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "codename" varchar(100) NOT NULL, "name" varchar(255) NOT NULL)

table.name: auth_user
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "auth_user" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "password" varchar(128) NOT NULL, "last_login" datetime NULL, "is_superuser" bool NOT NULL, "username" varchar(150) NOT NULL UNIQUE, "last_name" varchar(150) NOT NULL, "email" varchar(254) NOT NULL, "is_staff" bool NOT NULL, "is_active" bool NOT NULL, "date_joined" datetime NOT NULL, "first_name" varchar(150) NOT NULL)

table.name: auth_user_groups
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "auth_user_groups" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "user_id" integer NOT NULL REFERENCES "auth_user" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "group_id" integer NOT NULL REFERENCES "auth_group" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED)

table.name: auth_user_user_permissions
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "auth_user_user_permissions" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "user_id" integer NOT NULL REFERENCES "auth_user" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "permission_id" integer NOT NULL REFERENCES "auth_permission" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED)

table.name: django_admin_log
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "django_admin_log" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "object_id" text NULL, "object_repr" varchar(200) NOT NULL, "action_flag" smallint unsigned NOT NULL CHECK ("action_flag" >= 0), "change_message" text NOT NULL, "content_type_id" integer NULL REFERENCES "django_content_type" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "user_id" integer NOT NULL REFERENCES "auth_user" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "action_time" datetime NOT NULL)

table.name: django_content_type
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "django_content_type" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "app_label" varchar(100) NOT NULL, "model" varchar(100) NOT NULL)

table.name: django_migrations
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "django_migrations" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "app" varchar(255) NOT NULL, "name" varchar(255) NOT NULL, "applied" datetime NOT NULL)

table.name: django_session
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "django_session" ("session_key" varchar(40) NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY, "session_data" text NOT NULL, "expire_date" datetime NOT NULL)

table.name: punto_venta_boleta
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "punto_venta_boleta" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "fecha_modificacion" datetime NOT NULL, "fecha_creacion" datetime NOT NULL, "tipo_de_pago" varchar(25) NOT NULL, "monto_neto" integer unsigned NOT NULL CHECK ("monto_neto" >= 0), "monto_iva" integer unsigned NOT NULL CHECK ("monto_iva" >= 0), "cliente_id" integer NULL REFERENCES "punto_venta_cliente" ("persona_ptr_id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "empleado_id" integer NULL REFERENCES "punto_venta_empleado" ("persona_ptr_id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "monto_total" integer unsigned NOT NULL CHECK ("monto_total" >= 0))

table.name: punto_venta_boleta_producto
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "punto_venta_boleta_producto" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "fecha_modificacion" datetime NOT NULL, "fecha_creacion" datetime NOT NULL, "cantidad" integer unsigned NOT NULL CHECK ("cantidad" >= 0), "monto_neto" integer unsigned NOT NULL CHECK ("monto_neto" >= 0), "monto_iva" integer unsigned NOT NULL CHECK ("monto_iva" >= 0), "monto_total" integer unsigned NOT NULL CHECK ("monto_total" >= 0), "boleta_id" bigint NOT NULL REFERENCES "punto_venta_boleta" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "producto_id" bigint NULL REFERENCES "punto_venta_producto" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "precio_venta" integer unsigned NOT NULL CHECK ("precio_venta" >= 0))

table.name: punto_venta_boleta_servicio
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "punto_venta_boleta_servicio" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "fecha_modificacion" datetime NOT NULL, "fecha_creacion" datetime NOT NULL, "cantidad" integer unsigned NOT NULL CHECK ("cantidad" >= 0), "monto_neto" integer unsigned NOT NULL CHECK ("monto_neto" >= 0), "monto_iva" integer unsigned NOT NULL CHECK ("monto_iva" >= 0), "monto_total" integer unsigned NOT NULL CHECK ("monto_total" >= 0), "boleta_id" bigint NOT NULL REFERENCES "punto_venta_boleta" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "servicio_id" bigint NULL REFERENCES "punto_venta_servicio" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "precio_venta" integer unsigned NOT NULL CHECK ("precio_venta" >= 0))

table.name: punto_venta_cita
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "punto_venta_cita" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "fecha" date NOT NULL, "hora" time NOT NULL, "servicio_id" bigint NOT NULL REFERENCES "punto_venta_servicio" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "cliente_id" integer NULL REFERENCES "punto_venta_cliente" ("persona_ptr_id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED)

table.name: punto_venta_cliente
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "punto_venta_cliente" ("persona_ptr_id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY REFERENCES "punto_venta_persona" ("user_ptr_id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED)

table.name: punto_venta_empleado
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "punto_venta_empleado" ("persona_ptr_id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY REFERENCES "punto_venta_persona" ("user_ptr_id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "documento_identificador" varchar(30) NOT NULL, "fecha_contratacion" date NOT NULL, "afp" varchar(15) NOT NULL)

table.name: punto_venta_factura
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "punto_venta_factura" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "fecha_modificacion" datetime NOT NULL, "fecha_creacion" datetime NOT NULL, "numero_factura" integer unsigned NOT NULL CHECK ("numero_factura" >= 0), "tipo_de_pago" varchar(25) NOT NULL, "monto_neto" integer unsigned NOT NULL CHECK ("monto_neto" >= 0), "monto_iva" integer unsigned NOT NULL CHECK ("monto_iva" >= 0), "empleado_id" integer NOT NULL REFERENCES "auth_user" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "proveedor_id" bigint NULL REFERENCES "punto_venta_proveedor" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "monto_total" integer unsigned NOT NULL CHECK ("monto_total" >= 0))

table.name: punto_venta_factura_detalle
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "punto_venta_factura_detalle" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "fecha_modificacion" datetime NOT NULL, "fecha_creacion" datetime NOT NULL, "numero_factura" integer NOT NULL, "cantidad" integer unsigned NOT NULL CHECK ("cantidad" >= 0), "monto_neto" integer unsigned NOT NULL CHECK ("monto_neto" >= 0), "monto_iva" integer unsigned NOT NULL CHECK ("monto_iva" >= 0), "monto_total" integer unsigned NOT NULL CHECK ("monto_total" >= 0), "factura_id" bigint NOT NULL REFERENCES "punto_venta_factura" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "producto_id" bigint NULL REFERENCES "punto_venta_producto" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "precio_venta" integer unsigned NOT NULL CHECK ("precio_venta" >= 0))

table.name: punto_venta_persona
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "punto_venta_persona" ("user_ptr_id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY REFERENCES "auth_user" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "fecha_nacimiento" date NOT NULL, "direccion" varchar(20) NULL)

table.name: punto_venta_producto
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "punto_venta_producto" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "nombre" varchar(30) NOT NULL, "categoria" varchar(20) NOT NULL, "precio_compra" integer unsigned NOT NULL CHECK ("precio_compra" >= 0), "stock" integer unsigned NOT NULL CHECK ("stock" >= 0), "proveedor_id" bigint NOT NULL REFERENCES "punto_venta_proveedor" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "descripcion" varchar(50) NOT NULL, "imagen" varchar(100) NOT NULL, "precio_venta" integer unsigned NOT NULL CHECK ("precio_venta" >= 0))

table.name: punto_venta_proveedor
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "punto_venta_proveedor" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "nombre" varchar(40) NOT NULL, "direccion" varchar(40) NOT NULL, "rut_empresa" varchar(30) NOT NULL, "telefono_celular" varchar(30) NOT NULL, "email" varchar(40) NOT NULL)

table.name: punto_venta_servicio
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "punto_venta_servicio" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "nombre" varchar(30) NOT NULL, "descripcion" varchar(50) NOT NULL, "tiempo" bigint NOT NULL, "precio" integer unsigned NOT NULL CHECK ("precio" >= 0))

table.name: punto_venta_servicio_empleados
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "punto_venta_servicio_empleados" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "servicio_id" bigint NOT NULL REFERENCES "punto_venta_servicio" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "empleado_id" integer NOT NULL REFERENCES "punto_venta_empleado" ("persona_ptr_id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED)
